            <h1>Public administration</h1>
            <div class="temaMobIngressImg" style="display: none;"><img src="/Upload/PORTAL/Temabilder/offentlig_forvaltning_150x1.gif" alt="Shadows of people in discussion" /></div>
            <p class="textIngress">The Government wishes to maintain a strong and efficient public sector that provides the population with good services, based on freedom of choice and the right of co-determination. The public sector shall give adequate consideration to quality, accessibility, fairness and economic efficiency.</p>
            <img src="/Upload/PORTAL/Temabilder/offentlig_forvaltning_150x1.gif" alt="Shadows of people in discussion" class="temaIngressImg" />
            <div class="descriptionText"><p>The modernisation and development of the public sector affects many policy areas. <em>The Ministry of Modernisation,</em> which was established on 1 January 2006, is intended to be the coordinating ministry in the Government’s modernisation efforts. </p>
<p>On this page you will find general information and documents relating to public administration. You can explore this topic in more detail by using the menu on the right.</p></div>
