            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fad/pressesenter/pressemeldinger/2010/135-soker-om-over-28-millioner-kroner.html?id=604406" title="">
                        135 applications for more than NOK 28 million
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, Ministry of Government Administration, Reform and Church Affairs, 10.05.2010]</p>
                <p>- The response is overwhelming. This shows that the Norwegian web community is characterized by innovative power and will, creativity and knowledge, minister Rigmor Aasrud says.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
