                        Service for removal of web information launched
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[News story, Ministry of Government Administration, Reform and Church Affairs, 09.03.2010]</p>
                <p>Anybody who finds unwanted information about oneself on the internet is now able to contact the Norwegian Data Inspectorate’s new service slettmeg.no (“deleteme.no”) for advice.</p>
                
                
